{"ja522:0.1":"Jataka ","ja522:0.2":"Cattalisanipata ","ja522:0.3":"Tesakunavagga ","ja522:0.4":"2. Sarabhangajataka ","ja522:1.1":"“Alankata kundalino suvattha, ","ja522:1.2":"Veluriyamuttatharukhaggabandha; ","ja522:1.3":"Rathesabha titthatha ke nu tumhe, ","ja522:1.4":"Katham vo jananti manussaloke”. ","ja522:2.1":"“Ahamatthako bhimaratho panayam, ","ja522:2.2":"Kalingaraja pana uggatoyam; ","ja522:2.3":"Susannatanam isinam dassanaya, ","ja522:2.4":"Idhagata pucchitayemha panhe”. ","ja522:3.1":"“Vehayasam titthasi antalikkhe, ","ja522:3.2":"Pathaddhuno pannaraseva cando; ","ja522:3.3":"Pucchami tam yakkha mahanubhava, ","ja522:3.4":"Katham tam jananti manussaloke”. ","ja522:4.1":"“Yamahu devesu sujampatiti, ","ja522:4.2":"Maghavati tam ahu manussaloke; ","ja522:4.3":"Sa devaraja idamajja patto, ","ja522:4.4":"Susannatanam isinam dassanaya”. ","ja522:5.1":"“Dure suta no isayo samagata, ","ja522:5.2":"Mahiddhika iddhigunupapanna; ","ja522:5.3":"Vandami te ayire pasannacitto, ","ja522:5.4":"Ye jivalokettha manussasettha”. ","ja522:6.1":"“Gandho isinam ciradikkhitanam, ","ja522:6.2":"Kaya cuto gacchati malutena; ","ja522:6.3":"Ito patikkamma sahassanetta, ","ja522:6.4":"Gandho isinam asuci devaraja”. ","ja522:7.1":"“Gandho isinam ciradikkhitanam, ","ja522:7.2":"Kaya cuto gacchatu malutena; ","ja522:7.3":"Vicitrapuppham surabhimva malam, ","ja522:7.4":"Gandhanca etam patikankhama bhante; ","ja522:7.5":"Na hettha deva patikkulasannino”. ","ja522:8.1":"“Purindado bhutapati yasassi, ","ja522:8.2":"Devanamindo sakko maghava sujampati; ","ja522:8.3":"Sa devaraja asuraganappamaddano, ","ja522:8.4":"Okasamakankhati panha pucchitum. ","ja522:9.1":"Ko nevimesam idha panditanam, ","ja522:9.2":"Panhe puttho nipune byakarissati; ","ja522:9.3":"Tinnanca rannam manujadhipanam, ","ja522:9.4":"Devanamindassa ca vasavassa”. ","ja522:10.1":"“Ayam isi sarabhango tapassi, ","ja522:10.2":"Yato jato virato methunasma; ","ja522:10.3":"Aceraputto suvinitarupo, ","ja522:10.4":"So nesam panhani viyakarissati”. ","ja522:11.1":"“Kondanna panhani viyakarohi, ","ja522:11.2":"Yacanti tam isayo sadhurupa; ","ja522:11.3":"Kondanna eso manujesu dhammo, ","ja522:11.4":"Yam vuddhamagacchati esa bharo”. ","ja522:12.1":"“Katavakasa pucchantu bhonto, ","ja522:12.2":"Yam kinci panham manasabhipatthitam; ","ja522:12.3":"Ahanhi tam tam vo viyakarissam, ","ja522:12.4":"Natva sayam lokamimam paranca”. ","ja522:13.1":"Tato ca maghava sakko, ","ja522:13.2":"atthadassi purindado; ","ja522:13.3":"Apucchi pathamam panham, ","ja522:13.4":"yancasi abhipatthitam. ","ja522:14.1":"“Kim su vadhitva na kadaci socati, ","ja522:14.2":"Kissappahanam isayo vannayanti; ","ja522:14.3":"Kassidha vuttam pharusam khametha, ","ja522:14.4":"Akkhahi me kondanna etamattham”. ","ja522:15.1":"“Kodham vadhitva na kadaci socati, ","ja522:15.2":"Makkhappahanam isayo vannayanti; ","ja522:15.3":"Sabbesam vuttam pharusam khametha, ","ja522:15.4":"Etam khantim uttamamahu santo”. ","ja522:16.1":"“Sakka ubhinnam vacanam titikkhitum, ","ja522:16.2":"Sadisassa va setthatarassa vapi; ","ja522:16.3":"Katham nu hinassa vaco khametha, ","ja522:16.4":"Akkhahi me kondanna etamattham”. ","ja522:17.1":"“Bhaya hi setthassa vaco khametha, ","ja522:17.2":"Sarambhahetu pana sadisassa; ","ja522:17.3":"Yo cidha hinassa vaco khametha, ","ja522:17.4":"Etam khantim uttamamahu santo”. ","ja522:18.1":"“Katham vijanna catupattharupam, ","ja522:18.2":"Settham sarikkham athavapi hinam; ","ja522:18.3":"Viruparupena caranti santo, ","ja522:18.4":"Tasma hi sabbesam vaco khametha”. ","ja522:19.1":"“Na hetamattham mahatipi sena, ","ja522:19.2":"Sarajika yujjhamana labhetha; ","ja522:19.3":"Yam khantima sappuriso labhetha, ","ja522:19.4":"Khanti balassupasamanti vera”. ","ja522:20.1":"“Subhasitam te anumodiyana, ","ja522:20.2":"Annam tam pucchami tadingha bruhi; ","ja522:20.3":"Yatha ahum dandaki nalikero, ","ja522:20.4":"Athajjuno kalabu capi raja; ","ja522:20.5":"Tesam gatim bruhi supapakamminam, ","ja522:20.6":"Katthupapanna isinam vihethaka”. ","ja522:21.1":"“Kisanhi vaccham avakiriya dandaki, ","ja522:21.2":"Ucchinnamulo sajano sarattho; ","ja522:21.3":"Kukkulaname nirayamhi paccati, ","ja522:21.4":"Tassa phulingani patanti kaye. ","ja522:22.1":"Yo sannate pabbajite ahethayi, ","ja522:22.2":"Dhammam bhanante samane adusake; ","ja522:22.3":"Tam nalikeram sunakha parattha, ","ja522:22.4":"Sangamma khadanti viphandamanam. ","ja522:23.1":"Athajjuno niraye sattisule, ","ja522:23.2":"Avamsiro patito uddhampado; ","ja522:23.3":"Angirasam gotamam hethayitva, ","ja522:23.4":"Khantim tapassim cirabrahmacarim. ","ja522:24.1":"Yo khandaso pabbajitam achedayi, ","ja522:24.2":"Khantim vadantam samanam adusakam; ","ja522:24.3":"Kalabuvicim upapajja paccati, ","ja522:24.4":"Mahapatapam katukam bhayanakam. ","ja522:25.1":"Etani sutva nirayani pandito, ","ja522:25.2":"Annani papitthatarani cettha; ","ja522:25.3":"Dhammam care samanabrahmanesu, ","ja522:25.4":"Evankaro saggamupeti thanam”. ","ja522:26.1":"“Subhasitam te anumodiyana, ","ja522:26.2":"Annam tam pucchami tadingha bruhi; ","ja522:26.3":"Kathamvidham silavantam vadanti, ","ja522:26.4":"Kathamvidham pannavantam vadanti; ","ja522:26.5":"Kathamvidham sappurisam vadanti, ","ja522:26.6":"Kathamvidham no siri no jahati”. ","ja522:27.1":"“Kayena vacaya ca yodha sannato, ","ja522:27.2":"Manasa ca kinci na karoti papam; ","ja522:27.3":"Na attahetu alikam bhaneti, ","ja522:27.4":"Tathavidham silavantam vadanti. ","ja522:28.1":"Gambhirapanham manasabhicintayam, ","ja522:28.2":"Naccahitam kamma karoti luddam; ","ja522:28.3":"Kalagatam atthapadam na rincati, ","ja522:28.4":"Tathavidham pannavantam vadanti. ","ja522:29.1":"Yo ve katannu katavedi dhiro, ","ja522:29.2":"Kalyanamitto dalhabhatti ca hoti; ","ja522:29.3":"Dukhitassa sakkacca karoti kiccam, ","ja522:29.4":"Tathavidham sappurisam vadanti. ","ja522:30.1":"Etehi sabbehi gunehupeto, ","ja522:30.2":"Saddho mudu samvibhagi vadannu; ","ja522:30.3":"Sangahakam sakhilam sanhavacam, ","ja522:30.4":"Tathavidham no siri no jahati”. ","ja522:31.1":"“Subhasitam te anumodiyana, ","ja522:31.2":"Annam tam pucchami tadingha bruhi; ","ja522:31.3":"Silam sirincapi satanca dhammam, ","ja522:31.4":"Pannanca kam setthataram vadanti”. ","ja522:32.1":"“Panna hi settha kusala vadanti, ","ja522:32.2":"Nakkhattarajariva tarakanam; ","ja522:32.3":"Silam siri capi satanca dhammo, ","ja522:32.4":"Anvayika pannavato bhavanti”. ","ja522:33.1":"“Subhasitam te anumodiyana, ","ja522:33.2":"Annam tam pucchami tadingha bruhi; ","ja522:33.3":"Kathankaro kintikaro kimacaram, ","ja522:33.4":"Kim sevamano labhatidha pannam; ","ja522:33.5":"Pannaya dani patipadam vadehi, ","ja522:33.6":"Kathankaro pannava hoti macco”. ","ja522:34.1":"“Sevetha vuddhe nipune bahussute, ","ja522:34.2":"Uggahako ca paripucchako siya; ","ja522:34.3":"Suneyya sakkacca subhasitani, ","ja522:34.4":"Evankaro pannava hoti macco. ","ja522:35.1":"Sa pannava kamagune avekkhati, ","ja522:35.2":"Aniccato dukkhato rogato ca; ","ja522:35.3":"Evam vipassi pajahati chandam, ","ja522:35.4":"Dukkhesu kamesu mahabbhayesu. ","ja522:36.1":"Sa vitarago pavineyya dosam, ","ja522:36.2":"Mettam cittam bhavaye appamanam; ","ja522:36.3":"Sabbesu bhutesu nidhaya dandam, ","ja522:36.4":"Anindito brahmamupeti thanam”. ","ja522:37.1":"“Mahatthiyam agamanam ahosi, ","ja522:37.2":"Tavamatthaka bhimarathassa capi; ","ja522:37.3":"Kalingarajassa ca uggatassa, ","ja522:37.4":"Sabbesa vo kamarago pahino”. ","ja522:38.1":"“Evametam paracittavedi, ","ja522:38.2":"Sabbesa no kamarago pahino; ","ja522:38.3":"Karohi okasamanuggahaya, ","ja522:38.4":"Yatha gatim te abhisambhavema”. ","ja522:39.1":"“Karomi okasamanuggahaya, ","ja522:39.2":"Tatha hi vo kamarago pahino; ","ja522:39.3":"Pharatha kayam vipulaya pitiya, ","ja522:39.4":"Yatha gatim me abhisambhavetha”. ","ja522:40.1":"“Sabbam karissama tavanusasanim, ","ja522:40.2":"Yam yam tuvam vakkhasi bhuripanna; ","ja522:40.3":"Pharama kayam vipulaya pitiya, ","ja522:40.4":"Yatha gatim te abhisambhavema”. ","ja522:41.1":"“Kataya vacchassa kisassa puja, ","ja522:41.2":"Gacchantu bhonto isayo sadhurupa; ","ja522:41.3":"Jhane rata hotha sada samahita, ","ja522:41.4":"Esa rati pabbajitassa settha”. ","ja522:42.1":"Sutvana gatha paramatthasamhita, ","ja522:42.2":"Subhasita isina panditena; ","ja522:42.3":"Te vedajata anumodamana, ","ja522:42.4":"Pakkamu deva devapuram yasassino. ","ja522:43.1":"Gatha ima atthavati subyanjana, ","ja522:43.2":"Subhasita isina panditena; ","ja522:43.3":"Yo kocima atthikatva suneyya, ","ja522:43.4":"Labhetha pubbapariyam visesam; ","ja522:43.5":"Laddhana pubbapariyam visesam, ","ja522:43.6":"Adassanam maccurajassa gacche. ","ja522:44.1":"“Salissaro sariputto, ","ja522:44.2":"mendissaro ca kassapo; ","ja522:44.3":"Pabbato anuruddho ca, ","ja522:44.4":"kaccayano ca devalo. ","ja522:45.1":"Anusisso ca anando, ","ja522:45.2":"kisavaccho ca kolito; ","ja522:45.3":"Narado udayitthero, ","ja522:45.4":"parisa buddhaparisa; ","ja522:45.5":"Sarabhango lokanatho, ","ja522:45.6":"evam dharetha jatakan”ti. ","ja522:46.1":"Sarabhangajatakam dutiyam. "}